WEBVTT

00:01:15.159 --> 00:01:16.760
Ordinary net cafes just provide the machines

00:01:17.040 --> 00:01:18.560
They don't care at all if customers are tired,

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:19.439
hungry, thirsty, or bored.

00:01:19.760 --> 00:01:20.560
But in our net cafe,

00:01:20.920 --> 00:01:22.920
not only are the computers top-spec,

00:01:23.200 --> 00:01:24.400
but the experience is also top-tier.

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:25.519
What?

00:01:26.079 --> 00:01:27.680
Free snacks when you come to surf?

00:01:27.959 --> 00:01:28.920
And... and cola too?

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:30.959
Won't we lose a fortune?

00:01:30.959 --> 00:01:31.599
This is nothing.

00:01:31.959 --> 00:01:33.079
You don't know that in a dozen years,

00:01:33.079 --> 00:01:33.959
a hot pot restaurant

00:01:33.959 --> 00:01:36.079
will gain huge popularity just by focusing on service.

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:37.879
Many customers will be extremely satisfied.

00:01:38.159 --> 00:01:38.879
They'll make a killing.

00:01:38.879 --> 00:01:40.239
In a dozen years?

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:41.640
Brother Fan, what are you talking about?

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:43.760
Ah, the time doesn't matter.

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:46.120
What matters is we just learn the basics now.

00:01:46.120 --> 00:01:47.319
Give away some snacks and drinks.

00:01:47.319 --> 00:01:48.400
Once the customers are satisfied,

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:49.319
naturally, they'll come often.

00:01:49.439 --> 00:01:50.400
Are you afraid we won't earn it back?

00:01:52.359 --> 00:01:52.640
Mm.

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:54.959
Not only do we have snacks and drinks,

00:01:55.519 --> 00:01:56.840
we also provide simple meal services.

00:01:57.239 --> 00:01:57.760
Boss.

00:01:58.159 --> 00:01:59.480
Why is your set meal so expensive?

00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:00.519
Sixty-nine yuan.

00:02:00.519 --> 00:02:01.680
You'll know once you order it.

00:02:05.239 --> 00:02:05.879
Hello, brother.

00:02:06.439 --> 00:02:07.959
This is your VIP Love Set Meal.

00:02:09.159 --> 00:02:10.479
Boss, give me one too!

00:02:10.599 --> 00:02:11.319
Give me one too!

00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:13.639
Boss, I'll cover both lunch and dinner!

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:15.479
Besides the beautiful waitress delivery service,

00:02:15.639 --> 00:02:16.639
for competitive customers,

00:02:16.759 --> 00:02:18.439
we also offer professional gaming companion sets.

00:02:18.759 --> 00:02:19.759
They're all from the Computer Science Department,

00:02:19.759 --> 00:02:20.840
high-end talents I poached.

00:02:21.199 --> 00:02:23.439
One-on-one, hand-in-hand to help you rank up.

00:02:28.719 --> 00:02:29.199
We're here.

00:02:33.039 --> 00:02:34.879
I saw you busy with the net cafe these past few days.

00:02:34.879 --> 00:02:35.680
You were exhausted.

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:36.879
I didn't know how to help you.

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.000
Look.

00:02:38.759 --> 00:02:40.599
This is a secret base I found.

00:02:41.240 --> 00:02:41.560
Let's go.

00:02:42.280 --> 00:02:43.639
Let's go relax a bit.

00:02:43.639 --> 00:02:43.919
Let's go.

00:03:08.439 --> 00:03:09.080
Ruochu.

00:03:09.439 --> 00:03:10.759
Let's come here often in the future.

00:03:10.759 --> 00:03:11.520
Mm.

00:03:11.919 --> 00:03:13.159
We might not have the chance in the future.

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:14.960
Why?

00:03:14.960 --> 00:03:15.879
A few days ago in my class,

00:03:15.879 --> 00:03:17.400
during the Urban Planning lecture,

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:18.159
the teacher said

00:03:18.159 --> 00:03:18.800
that the neighborhood nearby

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:20.759
is the largest old district in Yunhai.

00:03:21.159 --> 00:03:23.080
It might all be demolished and rebuilt next year.

00:03:23.879 --> 00:03:24.960
Not just this amusement park,

00:03:25.599 --> 00:03:27.599
but the alleys and residential areas nearby

00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:28.719
might all be demolished.

00:03:29.520 --> 00:03:31.000
You mean this area is going to be demolished?

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:31.479
Yes.

00:03:34.159 --> 00:03:35.759
If not for you, no one would have reminded me.

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:38.479
You really are my lucky star.

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:44.479
Oh, alright.

00:03:50.439 --> 00:03:51.360
Our net cafe's warehouse

00:03:51.800 --> 00:03:52.599
has been turned into an office.

00:03:52.919 --> 00:03:53.520
Not bad, right?

00:03:53.879 --> 00:03:54.360
Looks pretty decent.

00:03:54.439 --> 00:03:54.879
You're here.

00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:55.479
Busy, huh?

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:04.319
These past few days, our internet cafe

00:04:04.560 --> 00:04:05.960
just from top-ups and membership fees,

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:06.919
we netted 32,000.

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:10.039
The daily net profit is no less than 8,000.

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:12.159
Let me show you.

00:04:12.719 --> 00:04:13.960
This is our revenue.

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.319
Impressive, right?

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:17.480
Brother Fan, strike while the iron is hot.

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.160
Should we open another internet cafe?

00:04:19.160 --> 00:04:20.240
Let's continue to grow bigger and stronger.

00:04:20.639 --> 00:04:23.079
We can't just stick to this one street.

00:04:23.079 --> 00:04:23.759
We have to step out.

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:24.759
Brother Liang,

00:04:24.920 --> 00:04:26.720
regarding this old city district,

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:27.959
are you familiar with the Yunmeng Park area?

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:28.600
I am.

00:04:29.240 --> 00:04:30.519
I grew up there.

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:32.399
There's been talk of developing it for a while,

00:04:32.399 --> 00:04:34.319
but the latest development documents haven't come down yet.

00:04:34.879 --> 00:04:36.160
Why? Let me check for you.

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:36.759
Check it out.

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:37.439
Okay.

00:04:40.040 --> 00:04:41.600
It is the year 2000 now.

00:04:41.759 --> 00:04:43.680
Real estate across the country is just taking off.

00:04:44.319 --> 00:04:45.759
If I can really secure that piece of land,

00:04:46.279 --> 00:04:47.240
in just a few years,

00:04:47.680 --> 00:04:49.639
I'll be a future real estate tycoon.

00:04:50.040 --> 00:04:52.240
It is reported that the Yanhai City People's Government

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:54.720
has passed the draft for rebuilding the Economic Zone.

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:57.680
Next year, the old district is a priority for development.

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:59.279
The Science and Technology Park will move in strongly.

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:06.360
This plot is in the city center.

00:05:06.639 --> 00:05:07.680
Such a prime location,

00:05:08.079 --> 00:05:09.480
I must find a way to buy it.

00:05:09.720 --> 00:05:10.639
Get out, all of you!

00:05:10.639 --> 00:05:11.759
Don't come bother me again!

00:05:12.879 --> 00:05:15.800
Can holding onto this broken park put food on the table?

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:18.000
Look at the equipment inside,

00:05:18.040 --> 00:05:19.560
it's all rusted and broken.

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:23.600
Sooner or later I'll tear it down to build offices.

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:24.600
You dare!

00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:28.439
Besides, when the demolition team comes,

00:05:28.439 --> 00:05:31.639
you won't even get half of this amount.

00:05:31.639 --> 00:05:33.399
Go, go, go, go, go, go.

00:05:35.399 --> 00:05:35.920
What are you doing?

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:36.879
Who are you?

00:05:37.959 --> 00:05:39.199
I advise you to mind your own business.

00:05:39.920 --> 00:05:41.519
Is bullying an old man considered "none of my business"?

00:05:41.519 --> 00:05:42.839
If you want to talk business, talk properly.

00:05:42.839 --> 00:05:43.879
What's the point of using force?

00:05:43.879 --> 00:05:46.319
I have nothing to discuss with this person.

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:49.959
You're also here to buy the land, right?

00:05:51.519 --> 00:05:52.319
Just you?

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:54.120
Look at your clothes.

00:05:54.480 --> 00:05:55.720
You can't even scrape together the deposit, can you?

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:57.319
Whether I can afford it is none of your business.

00:05:58.600 --> 00:06:00.279
I say, you people from Long's Real Estate,

00:06:00.920 --> 00:06:01.800
is this how you do business?

00:06:02.399 --> 00:06:03.439
If you use force again,

00:06:03.439 --> 00:06:04.839
I'm calling the police.

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:07.959
Just you wait.

00:06:13.079 --> 00:06:15.160
Young man, thank you.

00:06:15.360 --> 00:06:16.040
It was the right thing to do.

00:06:16.399 --> 00:06:17.560
Come in and have a cup of tea.

00:06:19.800 --> 00:06:20.560
Sir.

00:06:20.879 --> 00:06:21.800
To be honest,

00:06:21.800 --> 00:06:22.680
I came here today

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:24.160
because I also want to talk to you about the park.

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:28.000
You also want to buy this amusement park?

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:29.360
Yes.

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:31.519
But I'm different from that guy just now.

00:06:31.600 --> 00:06:32.399
If you are willing to sell,

00:06:32.639 --> 00:06:33.439
you set the price.

00:06:33.439 --> 00:06:34.439
I definitely won't lowball you.

00:06:34.480 --> 00:06:35.920
I won't flatten it to build office buildings either.

00:06:36.120 --> 00:06:37.199
Instead, I want to restore and rebuild it.

00:06:37.639 --> 00:06:39.600
Build some attractions that young people love.

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:42.480
Really?

00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:42.759
Yes.

00:06:49.319 --> 00:06:49.600
Here.

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:51.120
Pour it yourself.

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:51.800
Hey.

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:53.680
Dad.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:55.480
Hey.

00:06:55.759 --> 00:06:57.040
My daughter is back.

00:06:57.040 --> 00:06:58.120
Chen Fan.

00:06:58.199 --> 00:06:59.000
Sister Tang.

00:07:00.680 --> 00:07:01.279
Meiyun.

00:07:01.720 --> 00:07:02.759
This young man...

00:07:02.759 --> 00:07:04.439
...is the one who helped us drive away...

00:07:04.439 --> 00:07:07.040
...that hooligan manager from Long Real Estate.

00:07:07.839 --> 00:07:08.800
You two are...

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:09.959
This is my dad.

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:10.680
Oh my.

00:07:11.240 --> 00:07:13.360
Didn't I hear that people from Long's came to cause trouble...

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:14.439
...and injured my dad?

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:15.879
I came to bring my dad some medicine.

00:07:15.879 --> 00:07:17.720
Oh, my precious daughter is the best.

00:07:18.279 --> 00:07:19.800
She still knows how to care for her dad.

00:07:19.879 --> 00:07:21.360
I heard it all from my dad.

00:07:21.480 --> 00:07:23.199
That day, it was all thanks to you.

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:24.759
It's not easy for the old gentleman.

00:07:24.759 --> 00:07:26.079
Anyone who saw that would have helped.

00:07:26.759 --> 00:07:28.319
Dad, take good care of them.

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:28.639
Okay.

00:07:28.639 --> 00:07:29.439
Chen Fan, come here.

00:07:30.079 --> 00:07:31.199
Here, have some water.

00:07:33.199 --> 00:07:33.959
Have some tea, have some tea.

00:07:33.959 --> 00:07:35.360
How come I heard...

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:37.199
...that you're interested in this amusement park now?

00:07:37.600 --> 00:07:39.360
Why? Isn't the internet cafe keeping you busy enough?

00:07:39.360 --> 00:07:40.319
The internet cafe's traffic is stable.

00:07:40.319 --> 00:07:41.279
No need to worry about it.

00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:44.240
I am indeed somewhat interested in this amusement park.

00:07:44.680 --> 00:07:46.720
But if the old gentleman isn't willing to sell...

00:07:47.079 --> 00:07:47.759
...I won't force it.

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:49.680
About the internet cafe transfer last time...

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:50.680
...it was all thanks to you.

00:07:50.879 --> 00:07:52.920
If you hadn't taken over and given me funds to keep going...

00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:54.720
...I might still not have recovered by now.

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:59.079
How about I handle the amusement park matter?

00:07:59.160 --> 00:08:00.720
The old man listens to me the most.

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:01.639
I'll go persuade him.

00:08:01.759 --> 00:08:03.639
Oh, thank you so much, Sister Tang.

00:08:07.160 --> 00:08:08.120
This is the contract.

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:10.000
And this is the property deed for this land.

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:10.600
Take a look.

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:11.240
No need, Sister Tang.

00:08:11.680 --> 00:08:12.319
I trust you guys.

00:08:13.040 --> 00:08:14.360
Is the price okay?

00:08:15.240 --> 00:08:17.439
Your offer is already much higher than market price.

00:08:17.439 --> 00:08:19.000
We can't thank you enough.

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:20.879
The old gentleman worked hard to maintain it all these years.

00:08:20.959 --> 00:08:22.079
It's only right that he earns a bit more.

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:23.920
Then let's sign.

00:08:24.040 --> 00:08:24.439
Okay.

00:08:38.440 --> 00:08:40.279
The formalities are all complete now.

00:08:40.399 --> 00:08:41.639
Tomorrow I'll have the lawyer...

00:08:41.639 --> 00:08:41.919
Sister Tang.

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:42.360
Yeah?

00:08:42.840 --> 00:08:43.720
I have one more thing.

00:08:44.039 --> 00:08:45.519
Do you have any other conditions?

00:08:45.720 --> 00:08:46.360
It's not a condition.

00:08:47.720 --> 00:08:48.559
It's a request.

00:08:52.840 --> 00:08:53.679
What is it?

00:08:53.679 --> 00:08:55.399
We've been walking for so long and still haven't arrived.

00:09:01.720 --> 00:09:02.240
Three.

00:09:03.679 --> 00:09:04.159
Two.

00:09:05.720 --> 00:09:06.279
One.

00:09:06.519 --> 00:09:07.279
Open your eyes.

00:09:11.519 --> 00:09:14.440
Oh my god, it's so beautiful.

00:09:15.840 --> 00:09:16.639
Do you like it?

00:09:17.799 --> 00:09:18.679
I love it.

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:22.120
So this is the surprise you said you prepared for me.

00:09:25.960 --> 00:09:27.399
No matter what you want in the future...

00:09:27.879 --> 00:09:28.799
...or what you want to do...

00:09:29.519 --> 00:09:30.759
...I will make it happen for you.

00:09:31.679 --> 00:09:32.679
From today on...

00:09:33.519 --> 00:09:35.120
...not only will the Ferris wheel light up for you...

00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:37.559
...every step I take from now on...

00:09:38.600 --> 00:09:40.960
...is so I can stay by your side steadily...

00:09:41.919 --> 00:09:43.320
...to fulfill every wish you've spoken...

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:45.240
...and unspoken...

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:47.440
...every single one.

00:10:42.519 --> 00:10:43.559
Hello, Mr. Zhang.

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:47.039
Right now?

00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:50.759
Okay, I'll be right there.

00:10:52.559 --> 00:10:53.080
What's wrong?

00:10:53.080 --> 00:10:54.399
Mr. Zhang wants me back at school now.

00:10:54.399 --> 00:10:55.679
To discuss the group project.

00:10:57.519 --> 00:10:58.399
I'll take you back.

00:11:04.440 --> 00:11:06.279
Can I still come over in the future?

00:11:06.360 --> 00:11:06.960
Of course.

00:11:08.279 --> 00:11:11.320
I'll do anything my wifey asks.

00:11:12.360 --> 00:11:13.240
Smooth talker.

00:11:13.240 --> 00:11:13.559
Let's go.

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:16.919
Mr. Zhou.

00:11:16.919 --> 00:11:18.840
Yunhai is much more developed than Luocheng.

00:11:19.039 --> 00:11:19.879
And there are more college students.

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:20.600
There must be plenty of

00:11:20.600 --> 00:11:22.039
young people interested in computers.

00:11:22.279 --> 00:11:23.159
You should ask Chen Fan

00:11:23.159 --> 00:11:24.399
about just moving the computer school there.

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:30.320
Who was that just now?

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:31.200
Why didn't you answer?

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:31.840
Oh, it's nothing.

00:11:31.840 --> 00:11:32.399
The signal is bad.

00:11:32.399 --> 00:11:33.159
I'll call him back in a bit.

00:11:33.440 --> 00:11:34.120
Go on.

00:11:34.279 --> 00:11:36.279
Brother Fan, I still don't get it.

00:11:36.679 --> 00:11:38.440
Why did you spend a fortune

00:11:38.440 --> 00:11:41.360
to open a shabby amusement park in the old district?

00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:43.440
This lousy signal.

00:11:45.279 --> 00:11:46.120
Hey.

00:11:46.600 --> 00:11:48.120
I've been looking all over for you.

00:11:48.360 --> 00:11:49.679
And here you are drinking.